defaultWhilst we welc
defaultome the heat strategy, the TUC is concerned at the pace and scale of government support for industrial CCS. Rather than industrial and power CCS technologies developing in parallel, they appear to be moving forward in sequence. For example, there is no ind
defaultustrial mechanism in the Energy Bill to incentivise industrial CCS.
